videos.description: Dayton's Jalen Crutcher forces the turnover and finds Ibi Watson for the fast break lay-in.

videos.headline: Crutcher's steal leads to Watson's lay-in

videos.description: Jalen Crutcher shows his vision with a full-court pass to Obi Toppin, who lays it in for Dayton.

videos.description: Trey Landers drives hard to the basket and finishes with a vicious slam dunk.
